      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANYA BYPASS (2) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 5th (30.44) at Northam. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Can atone. SPEEDY CRUELLA (1) raced close to the lead throughout but collided with another runner, finishing a 4.5 lengths sixth (23.18) in a Grade 5/6 at this track. Gets chance to atone. BLACKPOOL VIPER (7) was below best at his last couple, the latest finishing seventh at this track, but was among the placings at this track three back. Expected to do much better this time. LANSLEY WHISPER (6) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
